The Bank Japan decide policy board meeting promote far rate liberalisation lower minimum denomination regulation-free deposit raise rate ceiling money market certificate (MMCs) central bank official said. The guideline effect April 6 bank said. Under guideline minimum denomination regulation-free deposit lower 100 mln yen 300 mln. The rate ceiling MMCs maturity 0.5 percentage below prevail certificate deposit rate bank said. But ceiling MMCs maturity remain 0.75 percentage below CD rates. The minimum denomination MMCs lower 10 mln yen 30 mln. The bank deposit rate lower 0.37 effective March 16 line half-point cut official discount rate February 23. New rate two-year one-year deposit bank example 3.64 pct 3.39 pct annum respectively. Demand deposit rate remain same. REUTER 